<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Farmácia</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f9ff;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #0078d4;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 10%;
        }

        header .logo {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 3em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        header nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        header nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .hero {
            background-color: #0078d4;
            padding: 40px 10%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            height: 60vh;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            color: white;
        }

        .hero .content {
            max-width: 50%;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .hero .buttons-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .hero .buttons-container button {
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #0078d4;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 2px solid #0078d4;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .hero .buttons-container button:hover {
            background-color: #0078d4;
            color: white;
        }

        .hero img {
            width: 600px;
            height: 400px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #0078d4;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">BioFarma</div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Soluções de Saúde para Você</h1>
            <p>Cuide da sua saúde com os melhores produtos e serviços farmacêuticos. Nossa equipe está aqui para oferecer assistência de qualidade e confiança.</p>
            <div class="buttons-container">
                <%= link_to "Caixa", new_venda_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
                <%= link_to "Lista Remédios", remedios_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
                <%= link_to "Exportar CSV", export_csv_vendas_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag("LOGO.png", alt: "Logo", width: "30", height: "30") %>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 BioFarma. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
